               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18030914-92-cd531" type="crimeDate">21st of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030914-92-off530 t18030914-92-cd531"></join>, a silver watch, value 3l. a seven-shilling piece, three shillings, and a farthing, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18030914-92-victim788" type="victimName">
                           Thomas 
                           Smith
                        <interp inst="t18030914-92-victim788" type="surname" value="Smith"></interp>
